t=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/jon_perl\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">Founder and President, Technology</div>\r\nJon started FoundOPS because of the great deal of potential he sees for the future for technology. He believes that the next revolution\r\nbelongs to small business. “Everyday we see technology breaking down barriers and making more resources available.” FoundOPS hopes to help\r\nsmall businesses harness the incredible resources and opportunities that are now available to them.\r\n\r\nAt 21, Jonathan may be young, but he is no newcomer to the world of business software. During high school Jonathan got his start working\r\nas software consultant for the service industry. In college, he knew the potential that existed for a small business software platform\r\nand began working on a solution. The prototypes he developed have become the precursor to FoundOPS.\r\n\r\nWhen asked what he likes to do in his free time, Jonathan responds “Free time?” Despite his borderline obsessive commitment to FoundOPS,\r\nJonathan still manages to sneak out of the office for the occasional bike ride or run. He’ll also read anything he can get his hands if\r\nhe thinks it will give him a bit of knowledge. One day Jonathan hopes to have some time to travel the world and just meet people but for\r\nnow he is happy right where he is.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<img id=\"orenImg\" src=\"../Content/Oren.png\" alt=\"Oren Shatken\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" />\r\n<div id=\"orenDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">Oren Shatken</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72288581\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/OrenShatken\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">Cofounder and President, Product</div>\r\nThe son of an artist and an architect, Oren has always been torn between the worlds of form and function. At Purdue, Oren studied\r\nan eclectic mix of Political Science, Art and Design, Entrepreneurship, Viticulture, and Jewish Studies. Eventually he was approached\r\nby Jonathan with an interesting application of both form and function. “From what I’ve seen, business enterprise software suffers from\r\nan impressive lack of both. These issues are the result of years of decision-makers at large corporations with the luxury of not having\r\nto use the software they were purchasing.”\r\n\r\nNow Oren believes user interface has emerged as one of the most significant considerations for the future. “Technology has progressed\r\nto such an advanced stage that the bottleneck has become the connection between technology and the users. Computers now wait for us\r\nmore than we wait for them.” By emphasizing simple and clean design practice, Oren hopes to create an interface that users will find\r\nintuitive and even addicting to use. “One day FoundOPS will be done when it does everything our users want and nothing else.”\r\n\r\nBeyond software, Oren loves spending time with his family and friends out on Shelter Island. An avid sailor, he claims his first crib\r\nwas the v-berth (the triangle shaped bed located in the very front of a boat) on his father’s Cape Dory sailboat. When the snow falls\r\noutside the FoundOPS office, Oren dreams about skiing, but he’s concerned his techniques has suffered since he moved out to Indiana.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<img id=\"zachImg\" src=\"../Content/Zach.png\" alt=\"Zach Bright\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" />\r\n<div id=\"zachDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">Zach Bright</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72290770\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/zbbright\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nSenior Software Engineer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nA die-hard Cubs fan, Zach hails from the suburbs of Chicago. At Purdue, Zach was a distinguished student of Computer Engineering,\r\nthe president of his fraternity, all while working as a teaching assistant. Working with an entire fraternity of men or a class\r\nfull of students taught Zach a great deal of patience. While Jon and Oren’s passion can create a great deal of excitement, we can\r\nalways rely on Zach’s calming disposition to maintain order at FoundOPS.\r\n\r\nZach loves getting outside on a nice day and playing a few holes of golf. He’ll be happy where ever he is in the world as long\r\nhe can tune in to watch the Cubs play.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<img id=\"andrewImg\" src=\"../Content/Andrew.png\" alt=\"Andrew Pohl\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" />\r\n<div id=\"andrewDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">Andrew Pohl</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=70782535\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/apohl1111\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nSilverlight Developer and Designer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nAndrew grew up in rural Indiana on a farm which might have something to do with his strong work ethic. “I leave work not when\r\nI’m tired, but when I’m done.” After earning his degree from Purdue in Computer Graphics Technology, Andrew joined the FoundOPS\r\nteam as a Silverlight developer and has been invaluable for creating the look and feel of the site.\r\n\r\nWhen he’s not working on the project, Andrew enjoys spending time outdoors and playing Ultimate Frisbee. Occasionally he can be\r\nfound kicking back and watching an action movie or two. His goals are modest but quickly becoming fulfilled; to be successful at something he enjoys.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<img id=\"ankitImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" alt=\"Ankit Buti\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" />\r\n<div id=\"ankitDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">Ankit Buti</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=62466824\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nAndroid Developer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nPerhaps it’s appropriate that FoundOPS mobile platform is developed by an engineer from who has traveled to us from the other side\r\nof the globe. Ankit grew up in New Delhi before coming to the states to attend college. He has always had a passion for mobile phone\r\ndevelopment and is especially excited about the Android platform.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<img id=\"johnImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" alt=\"John Mahoney\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" />\r\n<div id=\"johnDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">\r\n\r\nJohn Mahoney\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=42714775\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n<img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">Software Engineer</div>\r\nJohn was originally from Virginia before moving out to California to study aerospace engineering. Before joining the FoundOPS team,\r\nJohn worked in IT for a number of years. Nowadays, John is known as the algorithms guys and has been responsible for developing much\r\nof the logic that makes FoundOPS dispatching so efficient.\r\n\r\nIn his spare time, John can be found working with his hands on various construction projects. He also enjoys producing music. One day\r\nJohn hopes to turn his talents towards space exploration.\r\n\r\n</div>','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-3','','','2011-09-15 13:00:05','2011-09-15 17:00:05','',21,'http://localhost:15880/2011/09/15/21-revision-3/',0,'revision','',0),(28,1,'2011-09-15 13:07:01','2011-09-15 17:07:01','','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-4','','','2011-09-15 13:07:01','2011-09-15 17:07:01','',21,'http://localhost:15880/2011/09/15/21-revision-4/',0,'revision','',0),(29,1,'2011-09-15 13:07:19','2011-09-15 17:07:19','','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-5','','','2011-09-15 13:07:19','2011-09-15 17:07:19','',21,'http://localhost:15880/2011/09/15/21-revision-5/',0,'revision','',0),(30,1,'2011-09-15 13:11:20','2011-09-15 17:11:20','<style type=\"text\'css\">\r\n\r\n.tabs li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-12px;\r\n    left:-40px;\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: 1px solid White;\r\n    margin-bottom:5px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.tabs li a\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    left:20px;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs li a:hover, ul.tabs li a:active, ul.tabs li a:focus\r\n{\r\n    color:#ccc;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs a:link, ul.tabs a:visited\r\n{\r\n    color:#fff;\r\n}\r\n\r\n ul.tabs.homeTab\r\n {\r\n     border-top:none;\r\n }\r\n\r\n.subNav\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-5px;\r\n    background-color:#555;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.subNav li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:0px;\r\n    left:-20px;\r\n    height:25px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:normal;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: none;\r\n    margin-bottom:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ourTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-35px;\r\n    left:230px;\r\n    width:750px;\r\n    margin-bottom:100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n#navBoxTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-95px;\r\n    left:-220px;\r\n    height:150px;/*195 with subnav*/\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    background-color: #333335;\r\n    border:2px outset #666;\r\n    margin-bottom:-250px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.greyText\r\n{\r\n    color:#555;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.bigText\r\n{\r\n    font-size:18px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.links\r\n{\r\n    position:absolute;\r\n    top:30px;\r\n    margin-left:580px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg, #orenImg, #zachImg, #andrewImg, #ankitImg, #johnImg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:243px;\r\n    left:5px;\r\n    border: 4px solid #fff;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n    margin-top:-270px;\r\n    width:185px;\r\n    height:185px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg\r\n{\r\n    top:-17px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg, #orenBg, #zachBg, #andrewBg, #ankitBg, #johnBg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:260px;\r\n    left:0px;\r\n    width:203px;\r\n    height:203px;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg\r\n{\r\n    top:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #jonBg\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#659A41;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#orenBg, #orenBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#D9591E;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#zachBg, #zachBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#991A36;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewBg, #andrewBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#488FCD;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitBg, #ankitBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#E40000;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnBg, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#CE00CE;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #orenBar, #zachBar, #andrewBar, #ankitBar, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:10px;\r\n    left:-5px;\r\n    width:635px;\r\n    height:4px;\r\n    border-radius:2px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc, #orenDesc, #zachDesc, #andrewDesc, #ankitDesc, #johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n    top:60px;\r\n    left:260px;\r\n    width:630px;\r\n    margin-bottom:-200px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-top:-295px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-180px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-40px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<style/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id=\"ourTeam\">\r\n        <div id=\"navBoxTeam\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none\"><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Home\", \"Index\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Solution\", \"Product\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Company\", \"Company\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"The Team\", \"Team\", \"Home\")%>\r\n                    <%--<ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Members</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Advisors</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>--%>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"http://localhost:15880/\">Blog</a></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Contact Us\", \"ContactUs\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"jonBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"jonImg\" src=\"../Content/Jon.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Jonathan Perl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"jonDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Jonathan Perl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=40656805\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/jon_perl\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"jonBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Founder and President, Technology</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Jon started FoundOPS because of the great deal of potential he sees for the future for technology. He \r\n\r\nbelieves that the next revolution \r\n                belongs to small business. “Everyday we see technology breaking down barriers and making more resources \r\n\r\navailable.” FoundOPS hopes to help \r\n                small businesses harness the incredible resources and opportunities that are now available to them.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                At 21, Jonathan may be young, but he is no newcomer to the world of business software. During high school \r\n\r\nJonathan got his start working \r\n                as software consultant for the service industry. In college, he knew the potential that existed for a small \r\n\r\nbusiness software platform \r\n                and began working on a solution. The prototypes he developed have become the precursor to FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When asked what he likes to do in his free time, Jonathan responds “Free time?” Despite his borderline \r\n\r\nobsessive commitment to FoundOPS, \r\n                Jonathan still manages to sneak out of the office for the occasional bike ride or run. He’ll also read \r\n\r\nanything he can get his hands if \r\n                he thinks it will give him a bit of knowledge. One day Jonathan hopes to have some time to travel the world \r\n\r\nand just meet people but for \r\n                now he is happy right where he is.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"orenBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"orenImg\" src=\"../Content/Oren.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Oren Shatken\" />\r\n        <div id=\"orenDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Oren Shatken</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72288581\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a \r\n\r\nhref=\"http://twitter.com/#!/OrenShatken\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"orenBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Cofounder and President, Product</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                The son of an artist and an architect, Oren has always been torn between the worlds of form and function. \r\n\r\nAt Purdue, Oren studied \r\n                an eclectic mix of Political Science, Art and Design, Entrepreneurship, Viticulture, and Jewish Studies. \r\n\r\nEventually he was approached \r\n                by Jonathan with an interesting application of both form and function. “From what I’ve seen, business \r\n\r\nenterprise software suffers from \r\n                an impressive lack of both. These issues are the result of years of decision-makers at large corporations \r\n\r\nwith the luxury of not having \r\n                to use the software they were purchasing.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Now Oren believes user interface has emerged as one of the most significant considerations for the future. \r\n\r\n“Technology has progressed \r\n                to such an advanced stage that the bottleneck has become the connection between technology and the users. \r\n\r\nComputers now wait for us \r\n                more than we wait for them.” By emphasizing simple and clean design practice, Oren hopes to create an \r\n\r\ninterface that users will find \r\n                intuitive and even addicting to use. “One day FoundOPS will be done when it does everything our users want \r\n\r\nand nothing else.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Beyond software, Oren loves spending time with his family and friends out on Shelter Island. An avid \r\n\r\nsailor, he claims his first crib \r\n                was the v-berth (the triangle shaped bed located in the very front of a boat) on his father’s Cape Dory \r\n\r\nsailboat. When the snow falls \r\n                outside the FoundOPS office, Oren dreams about skiing, but he’s concerned his techniques has suffered since \r\n\r\nhe moved out to Indiana.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"zachBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"zachImg\" src=\"../Content/Zach.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Zach Bright\" />\r\n        <div id=\"zachDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Zach Bright</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72290770\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/zbbright\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"zachBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Senior Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                A die-hard Cubs fan, Zach hails from the suburbs of Chicago. At Purdue, Zach was a distinguished student of \r\n\r\nComputer Engineering, \r\n                the president of his fraternity, all while working as a teaching assistant. Working with an entire \r\n\r\nfraternity of men or a class \r\n                full of students taught Zach a great deal of patience. While Jon and Oren’s passion can create a great deal \r\n\r\nof excitement, we can \r\n                always rely on Zach’s calming disposition to maintain order at FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Zach loves getting outside on a nice day and playing a few holes of golf. He’ll be happy where ever he is \r\n\r\nin the world as long \r\n                he can tune in to watch the Cubs play.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"andrewBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"andrewImg\" src=\"../Content/Andrew.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Andrew Pohl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"andrewDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Andrew Pohl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=70782535\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/apohl1111\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"andrewBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Silverlight Developer and Designer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Andrew grew up in rural Indiana on a farm which might have something to do with his strong work ethic. “I \r\n\r\nleave work not when \r\n                I’m tired, but when I’m done.” After earning his degree from Purdue in Computer Graphics Technology, Andrew \r\n\r\njoined the FoundOPS \r\n                team as a Silverlight developer and has been invaluable for creating the look and feel of the site. </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When he’s not working on the project, Andrew enjoys spending time outdoors and playing Ultimate Frisbee. \r\n\r\nOccasionally he can be \r\n                found kicking back and watching an action movie or two. His goals are modest but quickly becoming \r\n\r\nfulfilled; to be successful at something he enjoys.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"ankitBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"ankitImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Ankit Buti\" />\r\n        <div id=\"ankitDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Ankit Buti</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=62466824\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"ankitBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Android Developer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Perhaps it’s appropriate that FoundOPS mobile platform is developed by an engineer from who has traveled to \r\n\r\nus from the other side \r\n                of the globe. Ankit grew up in New Delhi before coming to the states to attend college. He has always had a \r\n\r\npassion for mobile phone \r\n                development and is especially excited about the Android platform. \r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"johnBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"johnImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"John Mahoney\" />\r\n        <div id=\"johnDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    John Mahoney</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=42714775\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"johnBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                John was originally from Virginia before moving out to California to study aerospace engineering. Before \r\n\r\njoining the FoundOPS team, \r\n                John worked in IT for a number of years. Nowadays, John is known as the algorithms guys and has been \r\n\r\nresponsible for developing much \r\n                of the logic that makes FoundOPS dispatching so efficient.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                In his spare time, John can be found working with his hands on various construction projects. He also \r\n\r\nenjoys producing music. One day \r\n                John hopes to turn his talents towards space exploration.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-6','','','2011-09-15 13:11:20','2011-09-15 17:11:20','',21,'http://localhost:15880/2011/09/15/21-revision-6/',0,'revision','',0),(31,1,'2011-09-15 13:11:36','2011-09-15 17:11:36','<style type=\"text\'css\">\r\n\r\n.tabs li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-12px;\r\n    left:-40px;\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: 1px solid White;\r\n    margin-bottom:5px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.tabs li a\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    left:20px;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs li a:hover, ul.tabs li a:active, ul.tabs li a:focus\r\n{\r\n    color:#ccc;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs a:link, ul.tabs a:visited\r\n{\r\n    color:#fff;\r\n}\r\n\r\n ul.tabs.homeTab\r\n {\r\n     border-top:none;\r\n }\r\n\r\n.subNav\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-5px;\r\n    background-color:#555;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.subNav li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:0px;\r\n    left:-20px;\r\n    height:25px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:normal;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: none;\r\n    margin-bottom:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ourTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-35px;\r\n    left:230px;\r\n    width:750px;\r\n    margin-bottom:100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n#navBoxTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-95px;\r\n    left:-220px;\r\n    height:150px;/*195 with subnav*/\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    background-color: #333335;\r\n    border:2px outset #666;\r\n    margin-bottom:-250px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.greyText\r\n{\r\n    color:#555;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.bigText\r\n{\r\n    font-size:18px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.links\r\n{\r\n    position:absolute;\r\n    top:30px;\r\n    margin-left:580px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg, #orenImg, #zachImg, #andrewImg, #ankitImg, #johnImg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:243px;\r\n    left:5px;\r\n    border: 4px solid #fff;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n    margin-top:-270px;\r\n    width:185px;\r\n    height:185px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg\r\n{\r\n    top:-17px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg, #orenBg, #zachBg, #andrewBg, #ankitBg, #johnBg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:260px;\r\n    left:0px;\r\n    width:203px;\r\n    height:203px;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg\r\n{\r\n    top:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #jonBg\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#659A41;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#orenBg, #orenBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#D9591E;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#zachBg, #zachBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#991A36;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewBg, #andrewBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#488FCD;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitBg, #ankitBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#E40000;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnBg, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#CE00CE;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #orenBar, #zachBar, #andrewBar, #ankitBar, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:10px;\r\n    left:-5px;\r\n    width:635px;\r\n    height:4px;\r\n    border-radius:2px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc, #orenDesc, #zachDesc, #andrewDesc, #ankitDesc, #johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n    top:60px;\r\n    left:260px;\r\n    width:630px;\r\n    margin-bottom:-200px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-top:-295px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-180px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-40px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<style/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id=\"ourTeam\">\r\n        <div id=\"navBoxTeam\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none\"><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Home\", \"Index\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Solution\", \"Product\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Company\", \"Company\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"The Team\", \"Team\", \"Home\")%>\r\n                    <%--<ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Members</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Advisors</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>--%>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"http://localhost:15880/\">Blog</a></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Contact Us\", \"ContactUs\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"jonBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"jonImg\" src=\"../Content/Jon.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Jonathan Perl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"jonDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Jonathan Perl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=40656805\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/jon_perl\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"jonBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Founder and President, Technology</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Jon started FoundOPS because of the great deal of potential he sees for the future for technology. He \r\n\r\nbelieves that the next revolution \r\n                belongs to small business. “Everyday we see technology breaking down barriers and making more resources \r\n\r\navailable.” FoundOPS hopes to help \r\n                small businesses harness the incredible resources and opportunities that are now available to them.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                At 21, Jonathan may be young, but he is no newcomer to the world of business software. During high school \r\n\r\nJonathan got his start working \r\n                as software consultant for the service industry. In college, he knew the potential that existed for a small \r\n\r\nbusiness software platform \r\n                and began working on a solution. The prototypes he developed have become the precursor to FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When asked what he likes to do in his free time, Jonathan responds “Free time?” Despite his borderline \r\n\r\nobsessive commitment to FoundOPS, \r\n                Jonathan still manages to sneak out of the office for the occasional bike ride or run. He’ll also read \r\n\r\nanything he can get his hands if \r\n                he thinks it will give him a bit of knowledge. One day Jonathan hopes to have some time to travel the world \r\n\r\nand just meet people but for \r\n                now he is happy right where he is.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"orenBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"orenImg\" src=\"../Content/Oren.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Oren Shatken\" />\r\n        <div id=\"orenDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Oren Shatken</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72288581\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a \r\n\r\nhref=\"http://twitter.com/#!/OrenShatken\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"orenBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Cofounder and President, Product</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                The son of an artist and an architect, Oren has always been torn between the worlds of form and function. \r\n\r\nAt Purdue, Oren studied \r\n                an eclectic mix of Political Science, Art and Design, Entrepreneurship, Viticulture, and Jewish Studies. \r\n\r\nEventually he was approached \r\n                by Jonathan with an interesting application of both form and function. “From what I’ve seen, business \r\n\r\nenterprise software suffers from \r\n                an impressive lack of both. These issues are the result of years of decision-makers at large corporations \r\n\r\nwith the luxury of not having \r\n                to use the software they were purchasing.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Now Oren believes user interface has emerged as one of the most significant considerations for the future. \r\n\r\n“Technology has progressed \r\n                to such an advanced stage that the bottleneck has become the connection between technology and the users. \r\n\r\nComputers now wait for us \r\n                more than we wait for them.” By emphasizing simple and clean design practice, Oren hopes to create an \r\n\r\ninterface that users will find \r\n                intuitive and even addicting to use. “One day FoundOPS will be done when it does everything our users want \r\n\r\nand nothing else.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Beyond software, Oren loves spending time with his family and friends out on Shelter Island. An avid \r\n\r\nsailor, he claims his first crib \r\n                was the v-berth (the triangle shaped bed located in the very front of a boat) on his father’s Cape Dory \r\n\r\nsailboat. When the snow falls \r\n                outside the FoundOPS office, Oren dreams about skiing, but he’s concerned his techniques has suffered since \r\n\r\nhe moved out to Indiana.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"zachBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"zachImg\" src=\"../Content/Zach.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Zach Bright\" />\r\n        <div id=\"zachDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Zach Bright</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72290770\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/zbbright\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"zachBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Senior Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                A die-hard Cubs fan, Zach hails from the suburbs of Chicago. At Purdue, Zach was a distinguished student of \r\n\r\nComputer Engineering, \r\n                the president of his fraternity, all while working as a teaching assistant. Working with an entire \r\n\r\nfraternity of men or a class \r\n                full of students taught Zach a great deal of patience. While Jon and Oren’s passion can create a great deal \r\n\r\nof excitement, we can \r\n                always rely on Zach’s calming disposition to maintain order at FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Zach loves getting outside on a nice day and playing a few holes of golf. He’ll be happy where ever he is \r\n\r\nin the world as long \r\n                he can tune in to watch the Cubs play.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"andrewBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"andrewImg\" src=\"../Content/Andrew.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Andrew Pohl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"andrewDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Andrew Pohl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=70782535\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/apohl1111\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"andrewBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Silverlight Developer and Designer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Andrew grew up in rural Indiana on a farm which might have something to do with his strong work ethic. “I \r\n\r\nleave work not when \r\n                I’m tired, but when I’m done.” After earning his degree from Purdue in Computer Graphics Technology, Andrew \r\n\r\njoined the FoundOPS \r\n                team as a Silverlight developer and has been invaluable for creating the look and feel of the site. </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When he’s not working on the project, Andrew enjoys spending time outdoors and playing Ultimate Frisbee. \r\n\r\nOccasionally he can be \r\n                found kicking back and watching an action movie or two. His goals are modest but quickly becoming \r\n\r\nfulfilled; to be successful at something he enjoys.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"ankitBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"ankitImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Ankit Buti\" />\r\n        <div id=\"ankitDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Ankit Buti</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=62466824\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"ankitBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Android Developer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Perhaps it’s appropriate that FoundOPS mobile platform is developed by an engineer from who has traveled to \r\n\r\nus from the other side \r\n                of the globe. Ankit grew up in New Delhi before coming to the states to attend college. He has always had a \r\n\r\npassion for mobile phone \r\n                development and is especially excited about the Android platform. \r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"johnBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"johnImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"John Mahoney\" />\r\n        <div id=\"johnDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    John Mahoney</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=42714775\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"johnBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                John was originally from Virginia before moving out to California to study aerospace engineering. Before \r\n\r\njoining the FoundOPS team, \r\n                John worked in IT for a number of years. Nowadays, John is known as the algorithms guys and has been \r\n\r\nresponsible for developing much \r\n                of the logic that makes FoundOPS dispatching so efficient.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                In his spare time, John can be found working with his hands on various construction projects. He also \r\n\r\nenjoys producing music. One day \r\n                John hopes to turn his talents towards space exploration.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-7','','','2011-09-15 13:11:36','2011-09-15 17:11:36','',21,'http://localhost:15880/2011/09/15/21-revision-7/',0,'revision','',0),(32,1,'2011-09-15 13:11:46','2011-09-15 17:11:46','<style type=\"text\'css\">\r\n\r\n.tabs li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-12px;\r\n    left:-40px;\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: 1px solid White;\r\n    margin-bottom:5px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.tabs li a\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    left:20px;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs li a:hover, ul.tabs li a:active, ul.tabs li a:focus\r\n{\r\n    color:#ccc;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs a:link, ul.tabs a:visited\r\n{\r\n    color:#fff;\r\n}\r\n\r\n ul.tabs.homeTab\r\n {\r\n     border-top:none;\r\n }\r\n\r\n.subNav\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-5px;\r\n    background-color:#555;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.subNav li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:0px;\r\n    left:-20px;\r\n    height:25px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:normal;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: none;\r\n    margin-bottom:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ourTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-35px;\r\n    left:230px;\r\n    width:750px;\r\n    margin-bottom:100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n#navBoxTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-95px;\r\n    left:-220px;\r\n    height:150px;/*195 with subnav*/\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    background-color: #333335;\r\n    border:2px outset #666;\r\n    margin-bottom:-250px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.greyText\r\n{\r\n    color:#555;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.bigText\r\n{\r\n    font-size:18px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.links\r\n{\r\n    position:absolute;\r\n    top:30px;\r\n    margin-left:580px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg, #orenImg, #zachImg, #andrewImg, #ankitImg, #johnImg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:243px;\r\n    left:5px;\r\n    border: 4px solid #fff;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n    margin-top:-270px;\r\n    width:185px;\r\n    height:185px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg\r\n{\r\n    top:-17px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg, #orenBg, #zachBg, #andrewBg, #ankitBg, #johnBg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:260px;\r\n    left:0px;\r\n    width:203px;\r\n    height:203px;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg\r\n{\r\n    top:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #jonBg\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#659A41;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#orenBg, #orenBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#D9591E;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#zachBg, #zachBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#991A36;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewBg, #andrewBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#488FCD;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitBg, #ankitBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#E40000;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnBg, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#CE00CE;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #orenBar, #zachBar, #andrewBar, #ankitBar, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:10px;\r\n    left:-5px;\r\n    width:635px;\r\n    height:4px;\r\n    border-radius:2px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc, #orenDesc, #zachDesc, #andrewDesc, #ankitDesc, #johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n    top:60px;\r\n    left:260px;\r\n    width:630px;\r\n    margin-bottom:-200px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-top:-295px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-180px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-40px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<style/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id=\"ourTeam\">\r\n        <div id=\"navBoxTeam\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none\"><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Home\", \"Index\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Solution\", \"Product\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Company\", \"Company\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"The Team\", \"Team\", \"Home\")%>\r\n                    <%--<ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Members</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Advisors</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>--%>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"http://localhost:15880/\">Blog</a></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Contact Us\", \"ContactUs\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"jonBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"jonImg\" src=\"../Content/Jon.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Jonathan Perl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"jonDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Jonathan Perl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=40656805\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/jon_perl\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"jonBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Founder and President, Technology</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Jon started FoundOPS because of the great deal of potential he sees for the future for technology. He \r\n\r\nbelieves that the next revolution \r\n                belongs to small business. “Everyday we see technology breaking down barriers and making more resources \r\n\r\navailable.” FoundOPS hopes to help \r\n                small businesses harness the incredible resources and opportunities that are now available to them.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                At 21, Jonathan may be young, but he is no newcomer to the world of business software. During high school \r\n\r\nJonathan got his start working \r\n                as software consultant for the service industry. In college, he knew the potential that existed for a small \r\n\r\nbusiness software platform \r\n                and began working on a solution. The prototypes he developed have become the precursor to FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When asked what he likes to do in his free time, Jonathan responds “Free time?” Despite his borderline \r\n\r\nobsessive commitment to FoundOPS, \r\n                Jonathan still manages to sneak out of the office for the occasional bike ride or run. He’ll also read \r\n\r\nanything he can get his hands if \r\n                he thinks it will give him a bit of knowledge. One day Jonathan hopes to have some time to travel the world \r\n\r\nand just meet people but for \r\n                now he is happy right where he is.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"orenBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"orenImg\" src=\"../Content/Oren.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Oren Shatken\" />\r\n        <div id=\"orenDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Oren Shatken</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72288581\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a \r\n\r\nhref=\"http://twitter.com/#!/OrenShatken\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"orenBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Cofounder and President, Product</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                The son of an artist and an architect, Oren has always been torn between the worlds of form and function. \r\n\r\nAt Purdue, Oren studied \r\n                an eclectic mix of Political Science, Art and Design, Entrepreneurship, Viticulture, and Jewish Studies. \r\n\r\nEventually he was approached \r\n                by Jonathan with an interesting application of both form and function. “From what I’ve seen, business \r\n\r\nenterprise software suffers from \r\n                an impressive lack of both. These issues are the result of years of decision-makers at large corporations \r\n\r\nwith the luxury of not having \r\n                to use the software they were purchasing.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Now Oren believes user interface has emerged as one of the most significant considerations for the future. \r\n\r\n“Technology has progressed \r\n                to such an advanced stage that the bottleneck has become the connection between technology and the users. \r\n\r\nComputers now wait for us \r\n                more than we wait for them.” By emphasizing simple and clean design practice, Oren hopes to create an \r\n\r\ninterface that users will find \r\n                intuitive and even addicting to use. “One day FoundOPS will be done when it does everything our users want \r\n\r\nand nothing else.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Beyond software, Oren loves spending time with his family and friends out on Shelter Island. An avid \r\n\r\nsailor, he claims his first crib \r\n                was the v-berth (the triangle shaped bed located in the very front of a boat) on his father’s Cape Dory \r\n\r\nsailboat. When the snow falls \r\n                outside the FoundOPS office, Oren dreams about skiing, but he’s concerned his techniques has suffered since \r\n\r\nhe moved out to Indiana.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"zachBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"zachImg\" src=\"../Content/Zach.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Zach Bright\" />\r\n        <div id=\"zachDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Zach Bright</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72290770\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/zbbright\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"zachBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Senior Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                A die-hard Cubs fan, Zach hails from the suburbs of Chicago. At Purdue, Zach was a distinguished student of \r\n\r\nComputer Engineering, \r\n                the president of his fraternity, all while working as a teaching assistant. Working with an entire \r\n\r\nfraternity of men or a class \r\n                full of students taught Zach a great deal of patience. While Jon and Oren’s passion can create a great deal \r\n\r\nof excitement, we can \r\n                always rely on Zach’s calming disposition to maintain order at FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Zach loves getting outside on a nice day and playing a few holes of golf. He’ll be happy where ever he is \r\n\r\nin the world as long \r\n                he can tune in to watch the Cubs play.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"andrewBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"andrewImg\" src=\"../Content/Andrew.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Andrew Pohl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"andrewDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Andrew Pohl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=70782535\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/apohl1111\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"andrewBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Silverlight Developer and Designer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Andrew grew up in rural Indiana on a farm which might have something to do with his strong work ethic. “I \r\n\r\nleave work not when \r\n                I’m tired, but when I’m done.” After earning his degree from Purdue in Computer Graphics Technology, Andrew \r\n\r\njoined the FoundOPS \r\n                team as a Silverlight developer and has been invaluable for creating the look and feel of the site. </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When he’s not working on the project, Andrew enjoys spending time outdoors and playing Ultimate Frisbee. \r\n\r\nOccasionally he can be \r\n                found kicking back and watching an action movie or two. His goals are modest but quickly becoming \r\n\r\nfulfilled; to be successful at something he enjoys.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"ankitBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"ankitImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Ankit Buti\" />\r\n        <div id=\"ankitDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Ankit Buti</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=62466824\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"ankitBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Android Developer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Perhaps it’s appropriate that FoundOPS mobile platform is developed by an engineer from who has traveled to \r\n\r\nus from the other side \r\n                of the globe. Ankit grew up in New Delhi before coming to the states to attend college. He has always had a \r\n\r\npassion for mobile phone \r\n                development and is especially excited about the Android platform. \r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"johnBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"johnImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"John Mahoney\" />\r\n        <div id=\"johnDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    John Mahoney</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=42714775\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"johnBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                John was originally from Virginia before moving out to California to study aerospace engineering. Before \r\n\r\njoining the FoundOPS team, \r\n                John worked in IT for a number of years. Nowadays, John is known as the algorithms guys and has been \r\n\r\nresponsible for developing much \r\n                of the logic that makes FoundOPS dispatching so efficient.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                In his spare time, John can be found working with his hands on various construction projects. He also \r\n\r\nenjoys producing music. One day \r\n                John hopes to turn his talents towards space exploration.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-8','','','2011-09-15 13:11:46','2011-09-15 17:11:46','',21,'http://localhost:15880/2011/09/15/21-revision-8/',0,'revision','',0),(33,1,'2011-09-15 13:11:50','2011-09-15 17:11:50','<style type=\"text\'css\">\r\n\r\n.tabs li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-12px;\r\n    left:-40px;\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: 1px solid White;\r\n    margin-bottom:5px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.tabs li a\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    left:20px;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs li a:hover, ul.tabs li a:active, ul.tabs li a:focus\r\n{\r\n    color:#ccc;\r\n}\r\n\r\nul.tabs a:link, ul.tabs a:visited\r\n{\r\n    color:#fff;\r\n}\r\n\r\n ul.tabs.homeTab\r\n {\r\n     border-top:none;\r\n }\r\n\r\n.subNav\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-5px;\r\n    background-color:#555;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.subNav li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:0px;\r\n    left:-20px;\r\n    height:25px;\r\n    font-size:14px;\r\n    font-weight:normal;\r\n    list-style:none;\r\n    border-top: none;\r\n    margin-bottom:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ourTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-35px;\r\n    left:230px;\r\n    width:750px;\r\n    margin-bottom:100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n\r\n#navBoxTeam\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:-95px;\r\n    left:-220px;\r\n    height:150px;/*195 with subnav*/\r\n    width:170px;\r\n    background-color: #333335;\r\n    border:2px outset #666;\r\n    margin-bottom:-250px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.greyText\r\n{\r\n    color:#555;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.bigText\r\n{\r\n    font-size:18px;\r\n    font-weight:bold;\r\n}\r\n\r\n.links\r\n{\r\n    position:absolute;\r\n    top:30px;\r\n    margin-left:580px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg, #orenImg, #zachImg, #andrewImg, #ankitImg, #johnImg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:243px;\r\n    left:5px;\r\n    border: 4px solid #fff;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n    margin-top:-270px;\r\n    width:185px;\r\n    height:185px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonImg\r\n{\r\n    top:-17px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg, #orenBg, #zachBg, #andrewBg, #ankitBg, #johnBg\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:260px;\r\n    left:0px;\r\n    width:203px;\r\n    height:203px;\r\n    border-radius:15px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBg\r\n{\r\n    top:0px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #jonBg\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#659A41;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#orenBg, #orenBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#D9591E;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#zachBg, #zachBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#991A36;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewBg, #andrewBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#488FCD;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitBg, #ankitBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#E40000;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnBg, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    background-color:#CE00CE;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonBar, #orenBar, #zachBar, #andrewBar, #ankitBar, #johnBar\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    top:10px;\r\n    left:-5px;\r\n    width:635px;\r\n    height:4px;\r\n    border-radius:2px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc, #orenDesc, #zachDesc, #andrewDesc, #ankitDesc, #johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\n    margin-top:-35px;\r\n    top:60px;\r\n    left:260px;\r\n    width:630px;\r\n    margin-bottom:-200px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#jonDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-top:-295px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#andrewDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-180px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#ankitDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-100px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n#johnDesc\r\n{\r\n    margin-bottom:-40px;\r\n}\r\n\r\n<style/>\r\n\r\n\r\n<div id=\"ourTeam\">\r\n        <div id=\"navBoxTeam\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none\"><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Home\", \"Index\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Solution\", \"Product\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Our Company\", \"Company\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"The Team\", \"Team\", \"Home\")%>\r\n                    <%--<ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Members</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"#\">Advisors</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>--%>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"http://localhost:15880/\">Blog</a></li>\r\n                <li><%: Html.ActionLink(\"Contact Us\", \"ContactUs\", \"Home\")%></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"jonBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"jonImg\" src=\"../Content/Jon.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Jonathan Perl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"jonDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Jonathan Perl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=40656805\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/jon_perl\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"jonBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Founder and President, Technology</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Jon started FoundOPS because of the great deal of potential he sees for the future for technology. He \r\n\r\nbelieves that the next revolution \r\n                belongs to small business. “Everyday we see technology breaking down barriers and making more resources \r\n\r\navailable.” FoundOPS hopes to help \r\n                small businesses harness the incredible resources and opportunities that are now available to them.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                At 21, Jonathan may be young, but he is no newcomer to the world of business software. During high school \r\n\r\nJonathan got his start working \r\n                as software consultant for the service industry. In college, he knew the potential that existed for a small \r\n\r\nbusiness software platform \r\n                and began working on a solution. The prototypes he developed have become the precursor to FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When asked what he likes to do in his free time, Jonathan responds “Free time?” Despite his borderline \r\n\r\nobsessive commitment to FoundOPS, \r\n                Jonathan still manages to sneak out of the office for the occasional bike ride or run. He’ll also read \r\n\r\nanything he can get his hands if \r\n                he thinks it will give him a bit of knowledge. One day Jonathan hopes to have some time to travel the world \r\n\r\nand just meet people but for \r\n                now he is happy right where he is.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"orenBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"orenImg\" src=\"../Content/Oren.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Oren Shatken\" />\r\n        <div id=\"orenDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Oren Shatken</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72288581\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a \r\n\r\nhref=\"http://twitter.com/#!/OrenShatken\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"orenBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Cofounder and President, Product</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                The son of an artist and an architect, Oren has always been torn between the worlds of form and function. \r\n\r\nAt Purdue, Oren studied \r\n                an eclectic mix of Political Science, Art and Design, Entrepreneurship, Viticulture, and Jewish Studies. \r\n\r\nEventually he was approached \r\n                by Jonathan with an interesting application of both form and function. “From what I’ve seen, business \r\n\r\nenterprise software suffers from \r\n                an impressive lack of both. These issues are the result of years of decision-makers at large corporations \r\n\r\nwith the luxury of not having \r\n                to use the software they were purchasing.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Now Oren believes user interface has emerged as one of the most significant considerations for the future. \r\n\r\n“Technology has progressed \r\n                to such an advanced stage that the bottleneck has become the connection between technology and the users. \r\n\r\nComputers now wait for us \r\n                more than we wait for them.” By emphasizing simple and clean design practice, Oren hopes to create an \r\n\r\ninterface that users will find \r\n                intuitive and even addicting to use. “One day FoundOPS will be done when it does everything our users want \r\n\r\nand nothing else.”</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Beyond software, Oren loves spending time with his family and friends out on Shelter Island. An avid \r\n\r\nsailor, he claims his first crib \r\n                was the v-berth (the triangle shaped bed located in the very front of a boat) on his father’s Cape Dory \r\n\r\nsailboat. When the snow falls \r\n                outside the FoundOPS office, Oren dreams about skiing, but he’s concerned his techniques has suffered since \r\n\r\nhe moved out to Indiana.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"zachBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"zachImg\" src=\"../Content/Zach.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Zach Bright\" />\r\n        <div id=\"zachDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Zach Bright</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72290770\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/zbbright\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"zachBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Senior Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                A die-hard Cubs fan, Zach hails from the suburbs of Chicago. At Purdue, Zach was a distinguished student of \r\n\r\nComputer Engineering, \r\n                the president of his fraternity, all while working as a teaching assistant. Working with an entire \r\n\r\nfraternity of men or a class \r\n                full of students taught Zach a great deal of patience. While Jon and Oren’s passion can create a great deal \r\n\r\nof excitement, we can \r\n                always rely on Zach’s calming disposition to maintain order at FoundOPS.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Zach loves getting outside on a nice day and playing a few holes of golf. He’ll be happy where ever he is \r\n\r\nin the world as long \r\n                he can tune in to watch the Cubs play.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"andrewBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"andrewImg\" src=\"../Content/Andrew.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Andrew Pohl\" />\r\n        <div id=\"andrewDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Andrew Pohl</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=70782535\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/apohl1111\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"andrewBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Silverlight Developer and Designer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Andrew grew up in rural Indiana on a farm which might have something to do with his strong work ethic. “I \r\n\r\nleave work not when \r\n                I’m tired, but when I’m done.” After earning his degree from Purdue in Computer Graphics Technology, Andrew \r\n\r\njoined the FoundOPS \r\n                team as a Silverlight developer and has been invaluable for creating the look and feel of the site. </p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                When he’s not working on the project, Andrew enjoys spending time outdoors and playing Ultimate Frisbee. \r\n\r\nOccasionally he can be \r\n                found kicking back and watching an action movie or two. His goals are modest but quickly becoming \r\n\r\nfulfilled; to be successful at something he enjoys.</p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"ankitBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"ankitImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"Ankit Buti\" />\r\n        <div id=\"ankitDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Ankit Buti</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=62466824\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"ankitBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Android Developer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                Perhaps it’s appropriate that FoundOPS mobile platform is developed by an engineer from who has traveled to \r\n\r\nus from the other side \r\n                of the globe. Ankit grew up in New Delhi before coming to the states to attend college. He has always had a \r\n\r\npassion for mobile phone \r\n                development and is especially excited about the Android platform. \r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n        <div id=\"johnBg\">\r\n        </div>\r\n        <img id=\"johnImg\" src=\"../Content/BlankPhoto.png\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\" alt=\"John Mahoney\" />\r\n        <div id=\"johnDesc\">\r\n            <div class=\"bigText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    John Mahoney</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"links\">\r\n                <a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=42714775\">\r\n                    <img src=\"../Content/linkedin.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></a> <a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/FoundOps\">\r\n                        <img src=\"../Content/twitter.png\" border=\"0\" alt=\"\" /></a></div>\r\n            <div id=\"johnBar\">\r\n            </div>\r\n            <div class=\"greyText\">\r\n                <p>\r\n                    Software Engineer</p>\r\n            </div>\r\n            <p>\r\n                John was originally from Virginia before moving out to California to study aerospace engineering. Before \r\n\r\njoining the FoundOPS team, \r\n                John worked in IT for a number of years. Nowadays, John is known as the algorithms guys and has been \r\n\r\nresponsible for developing much \r\n                of the logic that makes FoundOPS dispatching so efficient.</p>\r\n            <p>\r\n                In his spare time, John can be found working with his hands on various construction projects. He also \r\n\r\nenjoys producing music. One day \r\n                John hopes to turn his talents towards space exploration.\r\n            </p>\r\n        </div>\r\n    </div>','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-9','','','2011-09-15 13:11:50','2011-09-15 17:11:50','',21,'http://localhost:15880/2011/09/15/21-revision-9/',0,'revision','',0),(34,1,'2011-09-15 13:12:29','2011-09-15 17:12:29','<style type=\"text\'css\">\r\n\r\n.tabs li\r\n{\r\n    position:relative;\r\