with his hands on various construction projects. He also enjoys producing music. One day John hopes to turn his talents towards space exploration.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-20','','','2011-09-23 12:33:46','2011-09-23 16:33:46','',21,'http://localhost:55206/2011/09/23/21-revision-20/',0,'revision','',0),(60,1,'2011-09-23 12:34:19','2011-09-23 16:34:19','<div style=\"position: relative; top: -55px; left: 300px; background: none; font-family: verdana; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<div id=\"navBoxTeam\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none;\"><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>\">Home</a></li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/beta\">FoundOPS</a></li>    \r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">About Us</a>\r\n                    <ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">The Team</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/values\">Our Values</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/jobs\">Jobs</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>/Home/ContactUs\">Contact Us</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<%= Global.RootBlogUrl %>\">Blog</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n<h1 class=\"title\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">The Team</h1>\r\n<div class=\"titleBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"titleText\">We’re young, committed, and lean (in our development methodology, not necessarily our body types).</div>\r\n<div id=\"jonBg\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"jonImg\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"jonDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">\r\n\r\nJonathan Perl\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"linkedin\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=40656805\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"twitter\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/jon_perl\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div></div>\r\n<div id=\"jonBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nFounder and President, Technology\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nJon started FoundOPS because of the great deal of potential he sees for the future for technology. He believes that the next revolution belongs to small business. “Everyday we see technology breaking down barriers and making more resources available.” FoundOPS hopes to help small businesses harness the incredible resources and opportunities that are now available to them.\r\n\r\nAt 21, Jonathan may be young, but he is no newcomer to the world of business software. During high school Jonathan got his start working as software consultant for the service industry. In college, he knew the potential that existed for a small business software platform and began working on a solution. The prototypes he developed have become the precursor to FoundOPS.\r\n\r\nWhen asked what he likes to do in his free time, Jonathan responds “Free time?” Despite his borderline obsessive commitment to FoundOPS, Jonathan still manages to sneak out of the office for the occasional bike ride or run. He’ll also read anything he can get his hands if he thinks it will give him a bit of knowledge. One day Jonathan hopes to have some time to travel the world and just meet people but for now he is happy right where he is.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"orenBg\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"orenImg\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"orenDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">\r\n\r\nOren Shatken\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"linkedin\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72288581\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"twitter\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/OrenShatken\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div></div>\r\n<div id=\"orenBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nCofounder and President, Product\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nThe son of an artist and an architect, Oren has always been torn between the worlds of form and function. At Purdue, Oren studied an eclectic mix of Political Science, Art and Design, Entrepreneurship, Viticulture, and Jewish Studies. Eventually he was approached by Jonathan with an interesting application of both form and function. “From what I’ve seen, business enterprise software suffers from an impressive lack of both. These issues are the result of years of decision-makers at large corporations with the luxury of not having to use the software they were purchasing.”\r\n\r\nNow Oren believes user interface has emerged as one of the most significant considerations for the future. “Technology has progressed to such an advanced stage that the bottleneck has become the connection between technology and the users. Computers now wait for us more than we wait for them.” By emphasizing simple and clean design practice, Oren hopes to create an interface that users will find intuitive and even addicting to use. “One day FoundOPS will be done when it does everything our users want and nothing else.”\r\n\r\nBeyond software, Oren loves spending time with his family and friends out on Shelter Island. An avid sailor, he claims his first crib was the v-berth (the triangle shaped bed located in the very front of a boat) on his father’s Cape Dory sailboat. When the snow falls outside the FoundOPS office, Oren dreams about skiing, but he’s concerned his techniques has suffered since he moved out to Indiana.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"zachBg\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"zachImg\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"zachDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">\r\n\r\nZach Bright\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"linkedin\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=72290770\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"twitter\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/zbbright\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div></div>\r\n<div id=\"zachBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nSenior Software Engineer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nA die-hard Cubs fan, Zach hails from the suburbs of Chicago. At Purdue, Zach was a distinguished student of Computer Engineering, the president of his fraternity, all while working as a teaching assistant. Working with an entire fraternity of men or a class full of students taught Zach a great deal of patience. While Jon and Oren’s passion can create a great deal of excitement, we can always rely on Zach’s calming disposition to maintain order at FoundOPS.\r\n\r\nZach loves getting outside on a nice day and playing a few holes of golf. He’ll be happy where ever he is in the world as long he can tune in to watch the Cubs play.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"andrewBg\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"andrewImg\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"andrewDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">\r\n\r\nAndrew Pohl\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"linkedin\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=70782535\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div><div class=\"twitter\"><a href=\"http://twitter.com/#!/apohl1111\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div></div>\r\n<div id=\"andrewBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nSilverlight Developer and Designer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nAndrew grew up in rural Indiana on a farm which might have something to do with his strong work ethic. “I leave work not when I’m tired, but when I’m done.” After earning his degree from Purdue in Computer Graphics Technology, Andrew joined the FoundOPS team as a Silverlight developer and has been invaluable for creating the look and feel of the site.\r\n\r\nWhen he’s not working on the project, Andrew enjoys spending time outdoors and playing Ultimate Frisbee. Occasionally he can be found kicking back and watching an action movie or two. His goals are modest but quickly becoming fulfilled; to be successful at something he enjoys.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"johnBg\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"johnImg\" width=\"242px\" height=\"242px\"></div>\r\n<div id=\"johnDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">\r\n\r\nJohn Mahoney\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div class=\"links\"><div class=\"linkedin\"><a href=\"http://www.linkedin.com/profile/view?id=42714775\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</a></div></div>\r\n<div id=\"johnBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"greyText\">\r\n\r\nSoftware Engineer\r\n\r\n</div>\r\nJohn was originally from Virginia before moving out to California to study aerospace engineering. Before joining the FoundOPS team, John worked in IT for a number of years. Nowadays, John is known as the algorithms guys and has been responsible for developing much of the logic that makes FoundOPS dispatching so efficient.\r\n\r\nIn his spare time, John can be found working with his hands on various construction projects. He also enjoys producing music. One day John hopes to turn his talents towards space exploration.\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','The Team','','inherit','open','open','','21-revision-21','','','2011-09-23 12:34:19','2011-09-23 16:34:19','',21,'http://localhost:55206/2011/09/23/21-revision-21/',0,'revision','',0),(61,1,'2011-09-23 12:35:48','2011-09-23 16:35:48','<div style=\"position: relative; top: -55px; left: 300px; background: none; font-family: verdana; font-size: 13px;\">\r\n<div id=\"navBoxTeam\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none;\"><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>\">Home</a></li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/beta\">FoundOPS</a></li>    \r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">About Us</a>\r\n                    <ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">The Team</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/values\">Our Values</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/jobs\">Jobs</a></li>\r\n  