to be proud Boilermakers. In addition, each year, FoundOPS offers a number of internship opportunities to the best and brightest Purdue students. We support local commerce and enjoy eating local produce and drinking local beer.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n<div id=\"IntegrityBg\"></div>\r\n<h1><img id=\"IntegrityImg\" src=\"http://localhost:31820/Content/Integrity.png\" alt=\"\" /></h1>\r\n<div id=\"IntegrityDesc\">\r\n<div class=\"bigText\">Integrity</div>\r\n<div id=\"IntegrityBar\"></div>\r\n<p>We’re still a small business ourselves with ambitions as lofty as those of our clients. However in our pursuit of smart growth, we vow to continue to maintain the highest standards of integrity and responsibility. In conjunction with the institutional measures we employ, we pride ourselves on the atmosphere of responsibility we’ve been able to maintain throughout the entire company. At FoundOPS, the ‘buck’ stops on every single employee’s desk.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Our Values','','inherit','open','open','','63-revision-2','','','2011-09-23 12:38:16','2011-09-23 16:38:16','',63,'http://localhost:55206/2011/09/23/63-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(66,1,'2011-09-23 12:41:19','2011-09-23 16:41:19','<div id=\"jobs\">\r\n<div id=\"navBoxJobs\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none;\"><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>\">Home</a></li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/beta\">FoundOPS</a></li>    \r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">About Us</a>\r\n                    <ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">The Team</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/values\">Our Values</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/jobs\">Jobs</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>/Home/ContactUs\">Contact Us</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>\">Blog</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n<h1 class=\"jobsTitle\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Jobs</h1>\r\n<div class=\"jobsTitleBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"jobsTitleText\">\r\n\r\n<p>FoundOPS is a growing company with opportunities for exceptional individuals. Right now we’re a tight team with uncompromising standards. Our work day stretches far beyond 9-5, but is interspersed with games of foosball, discussions of design philosophy, and a healthy dose of joking around. We are incredibly passionate about our project and are committed to producing results that the entire team is proud of. If you feel confident that you can not only meet, but exceed our expectations, we welcome you to send us an email (<a href=\"mailto:hr@foundops.com\">hr@foundops.com</a>). Generally speaking, we are more impressed with pet projects and portfolios then GPA’s and C.V.’s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Currently, FoundOPS is on the look out for people with experience in c#, silverlight, HTML5, integration with web services, and enterprise software marketing. However if there is some other way in which you think you might be able to contribute to our team, don’t hesitate to email us as well.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Jobs','','publish','open','open','','jobs','','','2011-09-23 12:42:25','2011-09-23 16:42:26','',0,'http://localhost:55206/?page_id=66',0,'page','',0),(67,1,'2011-09-23 12:41:14','2011-09-23 16:41:14','','Jobs','','inherit','open','open','','66-revision','','','2011-09-23 12:41:14','2011-09-23 16:41:14','',66,'http://localhost:55206/2011/09/23/66-revision/',0,'revision','',0),(68,1,'2011-09-23 12:41:19','2011-09-23 16:41:19','<div id=\"jobs\">\r\n<div id=\"navBoxJobs\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none;\"><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>\">Home</a></li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/beta\">FoundOPS</a></li>    \r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">About Us</a>\r\n                    <ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">The Team</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/values\">Our Values</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/jobs\">Jobs</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>/Home/ContactUs\">Contact Us</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n                </li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>\">Blog</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n<h1 class=\"contactUsTitle\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Jobs</h1>\r\n<div class=\"jobsTitleBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"jobsTitleText\">\r\n\r\n<p>FoundOPS is a growing company with opportunities for exceptional individuals. Right now we’re a tight team with uncompromising standards. Our work day stretches far beyond 9-5, but is interspersed with games of foosball, discussions of design philosophy, and a healthy dose of joking around. We are incredibly passionate about our project and are committed to producing results that the entire team is proud of. If you feel confident that you can not only meet, but exceed our expectations, we welcome you to send us an email (<a href=\"mailto:hr@foundops.com\">hr@foundops.com</a>). Generally speaking, we are more impressed with pet projects and portfolios then GPA’s and C.V.’s.</p>\r\n\r\n<p>Currently, FoundOPS is on the look out for people with experience in c#, silverlight, HTML5, integration with web services, and enterprise software marketing. However if there is some other way in which you think you might be able to contribute to our team, don’t hesitate to email us as well.</p>\r\n\r\n</div>\r\n</div>','Jobs','','inherit','open','open','','66-revision-2','','','2011-09-23 12:41:19','2011-09-23 16:41:19','',66,'http://localhost:55206/2011/09/23/66-revision-2/',0,'revision','',0),(69,1,'2011-09-23 12:50:37','2011-09-23 16:50:37','<div id=\"beta\">\r\n<div id=\"navBoxBeta\">\r\n            <ul class=\"tabs\">\r\n                <li style=\"border-top:none; margin-top:2px;\"><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>\">Home</a></li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/beta\">FoundOPS</a>\r\n			<ul class=\"subNav\">\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/beta\">Beta</a></li>\r\n                        <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"foundopsLink\"];?>/Home/Product\">Features</a></li>\r\n                    </ul>\r\n		</li>    \r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>/team\">About Us</a></li>\r\n                <li><a href=\"<?php echo $GLOBALS[\"blogLink\"];?>\">Blog</a></li>\r\n            </ul>\r\n        </div>\r\n<h1 class=\"betaTitle\" style=\"font-weight: normal;\">Beta</h1>\r\n<div class=\"betaTitleBar\"></div>\r\n<div class=\"jobsTitleText\">\r\n<p>Experienced entrepreneurs say that you fall in love with a problem first, then you innovate a solution. At FoundOPS, the problems we’ve fallen in love with are those facing small field service companies. Where are my technicians? What job am I going to next? Have all of my customers paid me? If you’ve ever managed a service team, you know how difficult these problems can be. Wouldn’t it be great if there was a system that helped you keep track of everything? It would be easy to setup and easier to use. You would be able log in through your computer and see exactly where your team was. Assigning jobs would be as simple as dragging and dropping. Technicians would see their next jobs on their mobile phones and be able to use turn-by-turn navigation to get their fast. And it would be cloud based so your data would be secure and you could access it from anywhere with an Internet connection. </p>\r\n<p>Sounds simple enough, right? So that’s what we’ve set out to do. It’s taken some time, a few pivots, but now we’re starting to see a pretty good system take face. However in order for it to become a great system, we know we need your help. Did we make the buttons on our mobile app big enough for you to use with your work gloves on? Is there some feature you just have to have? If shaping the next generation of service software sounds like something you might be interested in, complete the form below and we’ll get in contact with you.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n<form action=\"http://foundops.us2.list-manage.com/subscribe/post?u=6d3ef2a57e38d002d394a6527&amp;id=fd9a5afce8\" method=\"post\" id=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" name=\"mc-embedded-subscribe-form\" class=\"validate\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n	                    <h2>Beta Program Signup</h2>\r\n                        <div class=\"field\">\r\n<label for=\"mce-FNAME\">First Name</label><input type=\"text\" value=\"\" name=\"FNAME\" id=\"mce-FNAME\" />\r\n                            <label for=\"mce-LNAME\">Last Name</label><input type=\"text\" value=\"\" name=\"LNAME\" id=\"mce-LNAME\" />\r\n	                        <label for=\"mce-EMAIL\">Email Address (required)</label><input type=\"text\" value=\"\" name=\"EMAIL\" class=\"required email\" id=\"mce-EMAIL\" />\r\n                            <label for=\"mce-CNAME\">Company Name</label><input type=\"text\" value=\"\" name=\"CNAME\" id=\"mce-CNAME\" />\r\n<label for=\"mce-PHONE\">Phone</label><input type=\"text\" value=\"\" name=\"PHONE\" id=\"mce-PHONE\" />\r\n                        </div>\r\n	                    <div id=\"mce-responses\" class=\"clear\">\r\n		                    <div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-error-response\" style=\"display:none\"></div>\r\n		                    <div class=\"response\" id=\"mce-success-respo